{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_014dRcE5NcufyDnR7iLzfiBk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Both changes are in place. Here's the summary:\n\n---\n\n**PLANNER SUMMARY — pressyard**\n\n**Build strategy chosen**: `official_image` (WordPress official image + MariaDB dependency — already set in `registry/repos/pressyard.json`)\n\n**Files written / modified**:\n- `registry/auto-migration/queue.json` — state changed `build_failed` → `waiting_for_human`, added `human_request` with `kind: \"license\"`\n- `registry/repos/index.json` — added `\"pressyard\"` entry (was empty `{\"repos\": []}`, which would cause \"Config not found\" errors)\n\n**Files reviewed and left unchanged** (existing scaffold is correct):\n- `apps/pressyard/lzc-manifest.yml` — WordPress + MariaDB services, `registry.lazycat.cloud/...` image placeholders, `simple-inject-password` inject wired to `login_user`/`login_password` deploy params, correct `binds` for wp-content and mysql data dirs\n- `apps/pressyard/lzc-build.yml` — minimal but complete (`manifest`, `pkgout`, `icon`)\n- `apps/pressyard/lzc-deploy-params.yml` — `login_user`, `login_password`, `db_password`, `db_root_password` with `$random` defaults\n- `registry/repos/pressyard.json` — `enabled: false`, `migration_status: \"waiting_for_human\"`, correct official image + dependency config\n\n**Key decisions**:\n- Port: 80 (WordPress HTTP, internal container port)\n- Login route: `simple-inject-password` inject with deploy params (user must complete the WordPress install wizard on first launch using the generated credentials; subsequent logins auto-filled)\n- Data paths: `/lzcapp/var/data/pressyard/wp-content` for uploads/plugins/themes, `/lzcapp/var/db/pressyard/mysql` for MariaDB\n- Version: `1.5.0` (semver normalization of upstream `1.5-alpha.2`)\n\n**Waiting-for-human blocker flagged**:\n- **No LICENSE file** in upstream repo — hard block per SKILL.md. Human must approve before build can proceed.\n- Secondary concerns noted in `human_request.question`: suspicious repo structure (Roblox Lua script at root + actual code in ZIP archive), and architectural mismatch (PressYard is a multi-site management tool; scaffold deploys a single WordPress instance)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":139,"cache_read_input_tokens":67493,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":139},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8db3a375-e8d4-4eb3-8dc1-97d932784064","uuid":"db0ef084-1318-405c-9224-5b7ae9772f34"}
